beetle.translation[0].definitions[0].def: an insect with a round hard back that is usually black
beetle.translation[1].definitions[0].def: to go somewhere quickly and leaning forward
beetle.translation[1].definitions[0].exa: He went beetling off down the corridor.
beetle.translation[2].definitions[0].def: a small car made by Volkswagen which has a high, rounded top. It was first produced in the 1930s and has been popular ever since because of its unusual shape. In 1998 a Beetle with a completely new design went on sale.
